8-18 |accessdate=2020-09-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=氣象局將於晚上11時半發出八號風球 |url=https://www.tdm.com.mo/c_news/radio_news.php?id=482285 |agency=[[澳門電台|澳門電台]] |publisher=TDM [[澳廣視新聞|澳廣視新聞]] |date=2020-08-18 |accessdate=2020-08-29 |archive-date=2021-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106005458/https://www.tdm.com.mo/c_news/radio_news.php?id=482285 }}</ref>

