事後氣象局在專欄「天氣『FUN』識」中指出海高斯應為颱風級別<ref>{{Cite web|title=快閃十號！風暴潮錯峰？颱風海高斯之能量爆發|url=https://www.smg.gov.mo/zh/chat-info/340|accessdate=2020-08-20|publisher=澳門地球物理暨氣象局|archive-date=2021-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210817234548/https://www.smg.gov.mo/zh/chat-info/340}}</ref>。但在8月19日澳廣視午間新聞中名氣象局技術員葉婷婷誤稱海高斯在登陸前達強颱風級別<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tdm.com.mo/c_news/tv_news.php?id=482497|title=「海高斯」風力僅次「天鴿」|date=2020-08-19|publisher=澳門廣播電視股份有限公司|accessdate=2020-08-19|language=zh|archive-date=2021-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211024032751/https://www.tdm.com.mo/c_news/tv_news.php?id=482497}}</ref>。而在風暴吹襲後翌日，《[[澳門日報|澳門日報]]》在每篇文章報導，所定的級別均不一樣，分別有強烈熱帶風暴<ref>{{Cite web|title=風後居民唔使捱貴餸|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829020248/http://macaodaily.com/html/2020-08/20/content_1455648.htm|accessdate=2020-08-29|author=|date=|format=|work=澳門日報電子版|publisher=|language=}}</ref>、颱風<ref>{{Cite web|title=“海高斯”發威勁過“山竹”|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829020727/http://macaodaily.com/html/2020-08/20/content_1455538.htm|accessdate=2020-08-29|author=|date=2020-08-29|format=|work=web.archive.org|publisher=澳門日報電子版|language=}}</ref>、強颱風<ref>{{Cite web|title=強颱狂襲大步檻過|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829015951/http://macaodaily.com/html/2020-08/20/content_1455537.htm|accessdate=2020-08-29|author=|date=|format=|work=澳門日報電子版|publisher=|language=}}</ref>及超強颱風<ref>{{Cite web|title=氹仔多廈墮窗嚴重 團體促整治|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829020532/https://www.ugamm.org.mo/portal/ctr/cms/info/goToInfoView?info_id=2867db5e56ea43628284f2f769cfbbd7|accessdate=2020-08-29|date=2020-08-29|work=web.archive.org}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=氹仔多廈墮窗嚴重 團體促整治|url=http://macaodaily.com/html/2020-08/20/content_1455641.htm|accessdate=2020-08-29|author=|date=|format=|work=澳門日報電子版|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829015510/http://macaodaily.com/html/2020-08/20/content_1455641.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有文章更指出，海高斯的風速不足一天便從每小時20公里急升至每小時135公里。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=（此情可待）風雨中醒來|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829021229/http://macaodaily.com/html/2020-08/29/content_1457399.htm|accessdate=2020-08-29|author=|date=|format=|work=澳門日報電子版|publisher=|language=}}</ref>{{clear}}

